Enum Class ActionType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ActionType>
com.inFlight.shared.protocol.ActionType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ActionType>, Constable
public enum ActionType extends Enum<ActionType>
ActionType is an enum that defines the various actions that can be performed in the application. Each action corresponds to a specific operation that can be requested by the client or server.
